title: Michael Swanwick-Dragons of Babel
description:
The Title Dragons of Babel
Author Swanwick, Michael 
Genre FICTION / Fantasy  


Michael Swanwick is an icon within the fantasy community. The Dragons of Babel has drawn sterling reviews for its blend of magical elements with post-industrial atmosphere. After breaking his enslavement to a mechanical war dragon, Will le Fey winds up in the extraordinary city of Babel, where fairies of every type make their home. Trying to find his place, Will soon finds himself filling a leadership role
